%section.page-block
  .container
    %div{ style: 'padding:14px; background: #fff; border-radius: 14px; text-align: center;'}
      %h3
        홍길동님, 세상을 바꿀 준비되셨나요?
      %p.lead{ style: 'margin-top: 28px' }
        유형을 선택하세요.

      %p
        = link_to campaigns_path(wizard: 'petition'), method: :post, class: 'btn btn-lg btn-info btn-xs-block' do
          서명하기
        &nbsp;
        = link_to campaigns_path(wizard: 'picket'), method: :post, class: 'btn btn-lg btn-primary btn-xs-block' do
          팻말들기
        &nbsp;
        = link_to campaigns_path(wizard: 'sympathy'), method: :post, class: 'btn btn-lg btn-success btn-xs-block' do
          추모하기
        &nbsp;

